          <h2 class="about">ABOUT US</h2>
          <p class="breif">Welcome to AIIMS Vishram Sadan, a dedicated facility designed to provide comfort and care for patients and their families. Located within the premises of the prestigious All India Institute of Medical Sciences (AIIMS) in New Delhi, Vishram Sadan is committed to offering a serene and supportive environment for those undergoing medical treatment at AIIMS.</p>
