          <div class="section-title">
          <h2 class="about">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="breif">At AIIMS Vishram Sadan, our mission is to create a home away from home for patients and their families. We understand the challenges and stress that come with medical treatments, and our goal is to alleviate some of this burden by providing a peaceful and comfortable space for rest and recovery.</p>
        </div>
		<div class="section-title">
          <h2 class="about">Our Services</h2>
		 
          <p class="breif mb-1">Vishram Sadan offers a range of amenities and services to ensure the well-being and convenience of our guests, including:</p>
		    <div>
		 <ul><b>* Comfortable Accommodations:</b> Our facility includes clean, well-maintained rooms equipped with essential amenities to ensure a restful stay.</ul>
		 <ul><b>* 24/7 Support:</b> Our dedicated staff is available around the clock to assist with any needs or concerns, ensuring a safe and supportive environment</ul>
		 <ul><b>* Affordable Rates:</b> We offer accommodation at nominal charges, making it accessible for families from all walks of life.</ul>
		 </div>
        </div>
          <div class="section-title">
          <h2 class="about">Our Commitment</h2>
          <p class="breif">We are committed to maintaining the highest standards of cleanliness, safety, and hospitality. Our team works tirelessly to ensure that every guest experiences a comfortable and stress-free stay. We believe that a supportive environment can significantly contribute to the healing process, and we strive to create such an environment at AIIMS Vishram Sadan.</p>
        </div>
